messages.message:
Hi team,
I am seeing the following behavior while renaming files in the build on aihub.instabase.com (http://aihub.instabase.com). Is this expected?
Let's say the file name is 'file_name.pdf'. When you change the file name in the build to 'Sample File 1.pdf', it displays correctly as 'Sample File 1.pdf' when selecting sample files in the app info page. But, when we run the solution using the sample files, it changes the file names to something like "uniqueid__file_name.pdf" in the sample run output.
cc : @Shubham @Ananya @Rakshit
@Udit @Travis is it expected for sample file names to change when run through the app?
prob not, could you file a ticket @Pramod Munemanik
